Logger
------

either 
    make it elidable using annotation (http://www.scala-lang.org/api/current/index.html#scala.annotation.elidable)
or 
    use macro so that is can be omited at compile time using macro settings (http://www.scala-lang.org/api/2.11.1/scala-reflect/index.html#scala.reflect.macros.Infrastructure)
    macro can also allow more flexibility in the syntax ...

